short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: John Conway's game of life for your new tabs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you suffer from overpowering ennui when witnessing Google app icons every time you hit Command T?

Are you tired of looking at awe inspiring pictures of nature every time you open a new tab?

Surely you are fatigued by motivational quotes that seek to catalyze you towards making drastic changes to your life?

Why not have life itself!!!

Tab of life brings everyone’s favorite cellular automata, John Conway’s game of life to your new tabs. Sit entranced, mouth agape, at the incredible emergent complexity that the iterative application of simple rules brings.  

Now available at a Chrome Store near you!
